<Link id="l00596" /><CodeLine lineNumber="596"><Highlight kind="comment">/// An instruction propagated through the simulated instruction pipeline.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00597" /><CodeLine lineNumber="597"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00598" /><CodeLine lineNumber="598"><Highlight kind="comment">/// This class is used to monitor changes to the internal state of instructions</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00599" /><CodeLine lineNumber="599"><Highlight kind="comment">/// that are sent to the various components of the simulated hardware pipeline.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00600" /><CodeLine lineNumber="600" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mca/instruction"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">class </Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mca/instruction/#a103822ba234afb132cfe9c91c1bc5173">Instruction</a> : </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">public</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mca/instructionbase/#adf2552c33aa372b913e27996a97f73b5">InstructionBase</a> &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00601" /><CodeLine lineNumber="601"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">enum</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/instrstage">InstrStage</a> &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00602" /><CodeLine lineNumber="602"><Highlight kind="normal">    IS&#95;INVALID,    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Instruction in an invalid state.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00603" /><CodeLine lineNumber="603"><Highlight kind="normal">    IS&#95;DISPATCHED, </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Instruction dispatched but operands are not ready.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00604" /><CodeLine lineNumber="604"><Highlight kind="normal">    IS&#95;PENDING,    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Instruction is not ready, but operand latency is known.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00605" /><CodeLine lineNumber="605"><Highlight kind="normal">    IS&#95;READY,      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Instruction dispatched and operands ready.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00606" /><CodeLine lineNumber="606"><Highlight kind="normal">    IS&#95;EXECUTING,  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Instruction issued.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00607" /><CodeLine lineNumber="607"><Highlight kind="normal">    IS&#95;EXECUTED,   </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Instruction executed. Values are written back.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00608" /><CodeLine lineNumber="608"><Highlight kind="normal">    IS&#95;RETIRED     </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Instruction retired.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
